    "In this section, we derive the specific form of the reward gradient when the reward is parameterized by a critic LLM c ϕ.",
    "Recall from Eq.",
    "(A.2) that the gradient of the loss is:",
    "where we have approximated the optimal policy π θ ⋆ (ϕ) with the current policy π θ.",
    "We parameterize the reward using a binary classifier (critic) c ϕ (ℓ | a, q) where ℓ ∈ {expert, policy}: r ϕ (a, q) = c ϕ (ℓ = expert | a, q) -c ϕ (ℓ = policy | a, q)."
